# Musicly

A terminal-based music player for searching and playing songs from the command line.

## Installation

```bash
uvx musicly "All the stars"
```

## Usage

```bash
musicly play "song name"
musicly play "song name" --loop
```

## Requirements

- Python >= 3.13
